@jihoonkim87 The code was added to allow cross domain request on IE8/9.
Those browsers will not let you call xhr.open() for a cross domain url and it would throw Access is Denied error. The solution is to let that request go through by changing the url and then on xhr.send() it will be sent using flash which will work with CORS requests.

I fixed this at version 3.0.3 to throw the original error if the request is for not for this plugin's file upload.

